你-89歲。<br />\n<br />\n2082年，時間暫停器；我80歲，你-39歲。<br />\n<br />\n2120年，婚姻平權；我80歲，你8歲。<br />\n<br />\n2130年，時間布；我18歲，你18歲。<br />\n<br />\n110年後，終於能夠一起變老。"},{"pid":"94b7ee3fe8536d8e6404f0f345fe5294c16d9e44","tid":2348220,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bdd8152f66127702aa6e202b423f515243057a3","tid":2348220,"uid":342489,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"dc456155d3b398155938c71d04097ec6e5b24837","tid":2348220,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"哆啦A夢<br />\n同我<br />\n結婚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:27:11.000Z","msg":"哆啦A夢 同我 結婚<br />\n<br />\n2020年，初見；我18歲，你-91歲。<br />\n<br />\n2022年，相戀；我23歲，你-89歲。<br />\n<br />\n2082年，時間暫停器；我80歲，你-39歲。<br />\n<br />\n2120年，婚姻平權；我80歲，你8歲。<br />\n<br />\n2130年，時間布；我18歲，你18歲。<br />\n<br />\n110年後，終於能夠一起變老。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n但願我等到嗰一日"},{"pid":"eedf54089436cdb55d60f63c6b671f84891dd738","tid":2348220,"uid":342489,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e021e6eec1f1c93303ae8d9d0ede14cb9db3b3c1","tid":2348220,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:42:52.000Z","msg":"墓碑<br />\n薰衣草<br />\n她"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"墓碑 薰衣草 她<br />\n<br />\n明年暑假，一起去富良野吧。<br />\n<br />\n素來討厭千嬅紫的我，竟與她定下富良野之約。然而，行程尚未排滿，我的時間卻永遠定格在2020年12月31日。<br />\n<br />\n我看著她那柔和的側顏，卻無法伸手拭去她眼角的淚珠。抱歉，別哭；抱歉，這次我要失約了。"},{"pid":"62ac43fdc26c2943e8d64c2e13b21f44d7da72fb","tid":2348220,"uid":371769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"超時空  珊瑚  牛奶"},{"pid":"19ea18bd9e6a344dbd1c932f46f1798f6c0dc4c3","tid":2348220,"uid":355310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T16:38:16.000Z","msg":"連登創意台、你講我寫、極短篇故事產生器"},{"pid":"dcebefdbfb155e45b799fc1906bedeca0d88e17b","tid":2348220,"uid":342489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08da0b0eac26df5d91e6bb5e0facbdc537e98f64","tid":2348220,"uid":332128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"重陽節<br />\nIronman<br />\n林奠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"重陽節 Ironman 林奠<br />\n<br />\n《最無能》㐂娥<br />\n現金出糧愁永晝，瘋狂畀人咒。<br />\n佳節又重陽，去買廁紙，面皮成尺厚。<br />\n東尼打狗黃昏後，娥比屎坑臭。<br />\n莫道最無能，匪寇之流，罪魁禍之首。"},{"pid":"282d596e6f4a4b91e54da480defb511829de7e6a","tid":2348220,"uid":32223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:34:35.000Z","msg":"生果刀，番梘，牛角包"},{"pid":"01618b8bff902f6bc9dbd912f695b87486177224","tid":2348220,"uid":342489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5411d57b07c4befdb23c498fea3b40c9292b3cf2","tid":2348220,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:39:03.000Z","msg":"烏鴉 馴獸師 狼 <br />\n<br />\n再收集兩顆獸魂，就能夠轉職為幻獸師了。<br />\n<br />\n看著眼前一狼一鴉的組合，我決定採用最粗暴直接的方法&mdash;&mdash;瘋狂控制及拼命輸出。<br />\n<br />\n然而世事豈能盡如人意，我雖使出畢身絕學擊殺灰狼，但對黑鴉的攻擊卻以全MISS告終。<br />\n<br />\n30秒的CD時間，已經足以讓我死上十次八次。血量歸零那刻，我亦決定踏上課金這條不歸路。"},{"pid":"cea86ab054e9ab6dd113b85dfd2c2ff5751ee9f9","tid":2348220,"uid":16668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:39:21.000Z","msg":"電池，馬，單戀"},{"pid":"a4634443e3b3db353f9c3f63e0aef15617e8dc92","tid":2348220,"uid":370483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T17:54:57.000Z","msg":"月亮，冬，碼頭"},{"pid":"67cca4d2d896df85cd1854e04e03bc54edf47d76","tid":2348220,"uid":173847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"我<br />\n我女朋友<br />\n綠帽"},{"pid":"4f39bfc5ae4593e873ec6e639e46b2825caa0237","tid":2348220,"uid":342489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1deff85cc41622e231152da20ff8eec059d78b87","tid":2348220,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T14:50:42.000Z","msg":"烏鴉 石碑 黃昏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T18:19:05.000Z","msg":"烏鴉 石碑 黃昏<br />\n<br />\n馴獸師已被擊殺。<br />\n<br />\n我叫黑鴉，我從來沒有放棄奪回灰狼獸魂的理想。<br />\n<br />\n馴獸師已被擊殺。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼遊戲玩家可以無限復活，而灰狼就只能live once?<br />\n<br />\n遊戲為灰狼所立的石碑已經逐漸消失，憤怒不甘的情緒一湧而上，讓我失去理智。<br />\n<br />\n馴獸師已被擊殺。<br />\n馴獸師已被擊殺。<br />\n馴獸師已被擊殺。<br />\n馴獸師已被擊殺。<br />\n<br />\n你獲得【灰狼獸魂】<br />\n<br />\n我看著滿天彩霞，成功了⋯⋯嗎？<br />\n<br />\n你已被馴獸師擊殺。<br />\n<br />\n「終於可以轉職了，玩遊戲果然要課金啊！」"},{"pid":"874acd2b5078557f58f9f8fb2a8621e30714234f","tid":2348220,"uid":353591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T18:28:53.000Z","msg":"連登仔<br />\n雞<br />\n大波妹"}]}